attr.title: Wrestle Jump 2
attr.desc: Push the button to extend your wrestler's leg, smash your opponent's head to the ground to score, first to five wins!
attr.inst: Download the the game free from itch.io (https://ottoojala.itch.io/wrestle-jump-2), extract, and copy wrestlejump2.exe to the port's folder.
attr.inst_md: Download the game free from [itch.io](https://ottoojala.itch.io/wrestle-jump-2), extract, and copy `wrestlejump2.exe` to the port's folder.
